list_name: 1 Bed Condo for Rent in Willyn Ville
name: Willyn Ville
description:
Minimum term of 90 days stay ( URA compliance)
Swoop into Singapore’s alluring “Bohemian” enclave right in the heart of Holland Village. A hot spot for expatriates around the world, our modernly designed apartments, situated just beside Holland Village MRT and major bus-stops, features amenities that allow you to sit back, relax and take a breather.
The humble abode maintains its historic British Colonial flavour with its cool green exterior while holding true to a classic elegance throughout its interior. The impeccably clean and spacious room features a queen-sized bed, a work table, fresh linens, towels, spare toiletries, all fully provided for. Also stocked with all the cookware, dishware, kitchen towels, and condiments, our kitchen is ready for you to whip up budget-friendly meals when you are not out enjoying our fine local restaurants. Fully equipped with Optic Fibre Internet, work and play have never been made this easy!

The unit is a two-storey apartment with a total of 6 rooms. Each room is meant for single occupancy only and all my long term tenants are working professionals.

Situated directly beside Holland Village MRT and two major bus stations, our apartment also boasts of unparalleled convenience. Full condo facilities include Swimming pool, Club House, huge BBQ pit area, ample car park space, with adequate security at both the gate and back entrances. The walk-up two-storey maisonette is centrally located to the Island's best schools (RJC, ACJC, Instead, NUS, ACS International), Science and Tech hubs (Fusionopolis, Biopolis) and top research facilities.

Overview:
Room features:
- 1 queen-sized bed with shared bathroom
- Fully air-conditioned
- All windows can be opened (not locked)
- 100% cotton linen ready-made beds and fresh towels
- Hairdryer, iron, ironing board

Kitchen facilities:
- Full-sized fridge and freezer
- Toaster Oven
- Rice cooker
- Gas Stoves
- Fully-equipped with plates, cups, drinking glasses, wine glasses, plates, serving dishes, pots, pans, cutlery and crockery.

Other features:
- Full apartment cleaning once a fortnight. Common areas are cleaned weekly.
- 1-minute walk from Holland Village MRT station
- Minimum Stay Term 90 Days
- Fast and stable broadband Wi-Fi
- Washing machine
- Nearby shopping centres with a full range of amenities and services
- Key Operated Door lock system and access card system
- Cleaning products are available if you need them between cleaning sessions.

Contact Mark at  9128XXXX via whatsapp to arrange a viewing

description:
Minimum term of 90 days stay ( URA compliance)
Swoop into Singapore’s alluring “Bohemian” enclave right in the heart of Holland Village. A hot spot for expatriates around the world, our modernly designed apartments, situated just beside Holland Village MRT and major bus-stops, features amenities that allow you to sit back, relax and take a breather.
The humble abode maintains its historic British Colonial flavour with its cool green exterior while holding true to a classic elegance throughout its interior. The impeccably clean and spacious room features a queen-sized bed, a work table, fresh linens, towels, spare toiletries, all fully provided for. Also stocked with all the cookware, dishware, kitchen towels, and condiments, our kitchen is ready for you to whip up budget-friendly meals when you are not out enjoying our fine local restaurants. Fully equipped with Optic Fibre Internet, work and play have never been made this easy!

The unit is a two-storey apartment with a total of 6 rooms. Each room is meant for single occupancy only and all my long term tenants are working professionals.

Situated directly beside Holland Village MRT and two major bus stations, our apartment also boasts of unparalleled convenience. Full condo facilities include Swimming pool, Club House, huge BBQ pit area, ample car park space, with adequate security at both the gate and back entrances. The walk-up two-storey maisonette is centrally located to the Island's best schools (RJC, ACJC, Instead, NUS, ACS International), Science and Tech hubs (Fusionopolis, Biopolis) and top research facilities.

Room features:
- 1 queen-sized bed with shared bathroom

- Full-sized fridge and freezer

- Fully-equipped with plates, cups, drinking glasses, wine glasses, plates, serving dishes, pots, pans, cutlery and crockery.

- Minimum Stay Term 90 Days
- Fast and stable broadband Wi-Fi

- Key Operated Door lock system and access card system
- Cleaning products are available if you need them between cleaning sessions.
